		/// from a microphone. Whether or not you should send or receive data from the device (or both) depends on the type of device you are initializing which can be<br/>
		/// playback, capture, full-duplex or loopback. (Note that loopback mode is only supported on select backends.) Sending and receiving audio data to and from the<br/>
