		/// The desired size of a period in PCM frames. If this is 0, `periodSizeInMilliseconds` will be used instead. If both are 0 the default buffer size will<br/>
		/// be used depending on the selected performance profile. This value affects latency. See below for details.<br/>
		/// periodSizeInMilliseconds<br/>
		/// The desired size of a period in milliseconds. If this is 0, `periodSizeInFrames` will be used instead. If both are 0 the default buffer size will be<br/>
		/// used depending on the selected performance profile. The value affects latency. See below for details.<br/>
