		/// from the device object directly with `device.playback.channels`.<br/>
		/// playback.pChannelMap<br/>
		/// The channel map to use for playback. When left empty, the device's native channel map will be used. This can be retrieved after initialization from the<br/>
		/// device object direct with `device.playback.pChannelMap`. When set, the buffer should contain `channels` items.<br/>
