		/// PulseAudio only. Sets the stream name for playback.<br/>
		/// pulse.pStreamNameCapture<br/>
		/// PulseAudio only. Sets the stream name for capture.<br/>
		/// pulse.channelMap<br/>
		/// PulseAudio only. Sets the channel map that is requested from PulseAudio. See MA_PA_CHANNEL_MAP_* constants. Defaults to MA_PA_CHANNEL_MAP_AIFF.<br/>
